{"tid":2392704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"豪乳網紅「超兇對決」疑露暈走光！","createTime":"2021-02-03T03:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:43:04.000Z","uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85cb7b92089b8bd32fbf7e829fb873ff02159c92","tid":2392704,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"因為一張搭乘捷運的豪乳側拍，讓網紅「泥泥學姐」從素人一夕間成為高度關注對象，近期她更為了個人首本寫真書《泥是唯一：泥泥JANiE寫真書》勤跑宣傳，近日泥泥學姐和知名網紅Joeman合作拍片，不料在預告照片中，竟疑似露暈走光，讓泥泥學姐也親自現身回應！<br />\n<br />\n然而在預告照中，卻有網友赫然發現，「泥泥學姐」的豪乳前疑似露點，乳暈似乎不小心走光，因此紛紛留言提醒，隨後泥泥學姐也親自回覆「我們都保護的很好啦！是陰影而已～抱歉讓大家失望惹。」"},{"pid":"01c33fddf4d0fe33a9ccf0f79629ce6f11673845","tid":2392704,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"毫乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbfd876270aa8667e12fd8bd40184cce9782c70","tid":2392704,"uid":160437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"我入到嚟"},{"pid":"39f0c4ba9b40561a5d5d38c84cf230ca9cc12401","tid":2392704,"uid":33096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c5a2c2a122fbb0115fc699aec34e11b5767594","tid":2392704,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:26:06.000Z","msg":"你都訓咗幾耐吓"},{"pid":"fc316ea4027bbde001677ecd5205c3a9deaa9f59","tid":2392704,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:26:15.000Z","msg":"通常呢類無圖post,不用回覆由牠沈"},{"pid":"efcc3ecbfbd49d40f9d037211469b6c1a4971557","tid":2392704,"uid":65770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:30:02.00